  "name": "Lillian Frances Evolving FM Pad",
  "description": "Playable evolving FM pad inspired by the Kilohearts/Lillian Frances tutorial: soft sine-carrier FM, slowly opening harmonic motion, chorus-like width, filtered highs, light saturation, and a long spacious tail. \nWorks best in Octaves 3-5: a deep, low drone sound at octave 3, getting brighter and powerful in octave 4 to 5. \n",
